    <title>Bug #34 (Resolved): Running install of ODE seems to be having problems sending status updates</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://opendesignengine.net/issues/34"/>
    <id>http://opendesignengine.net/issues/34</id>
    <updated>2011-08-11T19:00:23+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>J. Simmons</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;I have noticed I am not getting emails when projects I am in have various updates (forum posts, wiki edits, etc), even when my email setting is: "For any event in all of my projects".  Note, I do have the check box "I don't want to be notified of changes that I make myself" checked, but I would still expect to see something when other people post.  I wonder if there is a cron job that should be running but is not.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
