    <title>Support #31 (Closed): Install SSL support to live ODE server</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://opendesignengine.net/issues/31"/>
    <id>http://opendesignengine.net/issues/31</id>
    <updated>2011-05-08T06:01:53+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>J. Simmons</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;Research, purchase, and configure a signed SSL cert.  Once done, configure http to redirect to https for all paths.  Be sure to test SVN over https.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
